dct_title_s: Bosnia and Herzegovina city graphic 1:12,500. Sarajevo. Series M903
dct_description_sm: Alternate title: Sarajevo, sheet 2-This sheet falls within NK 34-1, 1501, 1:250,000 and 2782 I, M709, 1:50,000. Transverse Mercator projection. Relief shown by 20 meter contour lintervals with supplementary 10 meter contours, and spot elevations. "Map information as of 1994. Street name information as of 1997." With a glossary. Reprinted by NIMA 5-00. "Coordinate conversion WGS 84 to ED 50.".
